NOTICE

This repository contains personal, general-purpose configuration files
("dotfiles") authored and maintained by Dmytro Soltysiuk.

These files are intended for use across multiple operating systems and
hardware environments and are not specific to any employer, client,
project, or internal system.

Host-specific configuration data may be included to adapt behavior to
different machines (e.g., hardware capabilities, OS defaults, user
preferences). Such data:
- contains no proprietary logic, algorithms, or workflows;
- contains no confidential, internal, or employer-specific information;
- is provided solely as configuration parameters consumed by the
  general-purpose code in this repository.

No employer is granted ownership of this repository or its contents by
virtue of execution, use, or modification on employer-provided hardware,
except as required by applicable law or written agreement.
